    "body" : "<pre><code>$whereis java\njava: /usr/bin/java /usr/bin/X11/java /usr/share/java     /usr/share/man/man1/java.1.gz\n$cd /usr/bin\n$ls -l java\nlrwxrwxrwx 1 root root 22 Apr 15  2014 java -&gt; /etc/alternatives/java\n$ls -l /etc/alternatives/java\nlrwxrwxrwx 1 root root 39 Apr 15  2014 /etc/alternatives/java -&gt;     /usr/lib/jvm/java-7-oracle/jre/bin/java\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>So,JDK's real location is  <code>/usr/lib/jvm/java-7-oracle/</code></p>\n"
