    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>I am using Ubuntu 18.04.1 LTS. In my case I had to open the file:</p>\n\n<pre><code>/home/[username]/netbeans-8.2/etc/netbeans.conf\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>And change the jdk location to:</p>\n\n<pre><code>netbeans_jdkhome=\"/opt/jdk/jdk1.8.0_152\"\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Then saved the file and re-run Netbeans. It worked for me.</p>\n"
